
noc.schema:  contains db `noc` schema


backup db `noc`:
=================

esv4-db03.corp:lwang[587] ~/db_backup $ cat backup_db_noc 
#!/bin/bash
/usr/local/mysql/bin/mysqldump -u <user>  --password=<pwd>  noc  > /export/home/lwang/db_backup/noc.dump.`date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S` 



put in cron:

# backup mysql db `noc`
28 08 * * 1-5 /export/home/lwang/db_backup/backup_db_noc  >/dev/null 2>&1



